msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:3.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""
"When they’ve gone forth they generate possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "mn29:3.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attamano hoti na paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re not happy with that, and haven’t got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn29:3.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "They don’t glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn29:3.7"
msgid ""
"So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na majjati nappamajjati na pamādaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"Nor do they become indulgent and fall into negligence regarding those "
"possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "mn29:3.8"
msgid "Appamatto samāno sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr "Being diligent, they become accomplished in ethics."

msgctxt "mn29:3.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re happy with that, and they’ve got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn29:3.10"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that:"

msgctxt "mn29:3.11"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo, ime panaññe bhikkhū dussīlā pāpadhammā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’m the one who is ethical, of good character. These other mendicants are "
"unethical, of bad character.’"

msgctxt "mn29:3.12"
msgid ""
"So tāya sīlasampadāya majjati pamajjati pamādaṃ āpajjati, pamatto samāno "
"dukkhaṃ viharati."
msgstr ""
"And so they become indulgent and fall into negligence regarding their "
"accomplishment in ethics. And being negligent they live in suffering."

