msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tacaṃ aggahesi brahmacariyassa;"
msgstr ""
"This is called a mendicant who has grabbed the bark of the spiritual life"

msgctxt "mn29:9.16"
msgid "tena ca vosānaṃ āpādi."
msgstr "and stopped short with that."

